snippet.title: Tiger-Heli (NES) - Player 1 Going For 1 Run
snippet.description:
What do you do if you want to play everything in a lifetime? 
Player 1 Going For 1 Run is a project where I play each game for only one run.

I play this game until I'm Game Over, or until I complete it.
